overview: Nina alias #Ninalabiche on snap, is a young girl addicted to social networks. To escape her anxieties and her lack of confidence, she invents a life with a doe filter on her phone. Nina is in love with Jonas, a boy on the internet whom she harasses. One day, when she bombards the canvas with her snaps, the virtual meets the real, Nina meets the doe and maybe even the one she loves so much ...
title: I am a doe
